data.description: Welcome home! This stunning 4 bed/ 2 bath home is nestled in the highly sought-after Summerhaven neighborhood of Debary, FL. Close to I-4 for a 45-minute drive to Disney or Daytona Beach. Recent upgrades include a new A/C 11/22, Roof 7/20, kitchen cabinets, countertops, & appliances, ADA toilets, electric outlets & switches, and custom-built closets for extra storage. The interior boasts an abundance of natural light streaming in through skylights across the kitchen and living room, and 4 sets of french doors leading out to a screened-in lanai overlooking fruit trees scattered around the fenced backyard. Cozy up to one of two fireplaces or spread out in the massive resort-style master suite, large enough for 2 queen-sized beds! Don't miss out on the 2-car garage and oversized driveway with ample space for all your vehicles and toys. The washer, Dryer, and the spare refrigerator do not convey. PRICED TO SELL. Schedule a showing with your agent today - Don't miss out on a chance to make this house your home!
